Installation Instructions
-------------------------

Dependencies:
    A Perl 5 interpreter
    Package DBD::SQLite3 (provided by libdbd-sqlite3-perl on Debian systems)

To install to the system path:
    Run the install script in install_linux.sh or install_win.bat,
    depending on your operating system.

To run:
    Type bookdblite in the command-line. It should then run as expected.
